NAME
  TYPE - Display file contents (Internal)

SYNOPSIS
  TYPE [file]

DESCRIPTION
  Displays the contents of a file.
  If the file extension is .BIN, it
  displays a hex dump.
  
  This is an internal command. For
  large files, consider using CAT.

EXAMPLES
  TYPE README.TXT
  TYPE PROG.BIN

SEE ALSO
  CAT, HEAD, TAIL, HEX